<br>
<br>
On yet ANOTHER topic, people talking about nuking at 98% with SoS while nuking at 98% with a Draught won't pull aggro... WELL NO DUH.  Think about it... Consider SoS as 3 Draughts. It's only 110 damage less.<br>
2.3 cast Draught<br>
2.25 recast<br>
2.3 cast Draught<br>
2.25 recast<br>
2.3 cast Draught<br>
<br>
That's 11.4 seconds.  Now, consider a 6 second SoS.  Let the mob hit 98%, then WAIT 5.4 seconds.  Ooo... guess what? Did that mob's life just drop another 4%!?!  Throw out a SoS at 94% and you have a LOT better chance of not getting summoned.  And chaining 3 draughts together from 98% has a pretty decent chance of getting you summoned too if your tank hasn't procced EB.<br>
Why would you even start with a draught?  At 97% or so I through out an ADoI (or Ice Spear) which is a better mana/damage ratio... then throw out a couple concussions... and you're set!<br>
<br>
Screw draughts, they just aren't mana efficient anymore.<br>
